{"tid":711041,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"VBA求教-loop and varible","createTime":"2018-06-21T08:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T10:47:22.000Z","uid":168540,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b9bc9b64f4d1d379539a8d5cb118aae231fc13e6","tid":711041,"uid":168540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:43:47.000Z","msg":"A  B  C   ..   X<br />\n100  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想整個For loop 想個格仔既 reference 跟住郁可以點整,EG :<br />\nA100=  sum (A1:A99)<br />\nB100= sum (B2:B99)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我識LET左邊做用CELL(i,&quot;A&quot;).value就控到, 但右邊唔識寫。<br />\n<br />\n有冇大佬可以幫幫手, 講個Keyword 都OK<br />\n<br />\n暫時我用code copy and paste 當做到, 我想用D聰明少少既做法, 感謝萬分"},{"pid":"c4c55db2300d66005f2aa81fd534b3484e194443","tid":711041,"uid":43724,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:50:52.000Z","msg":"想幫但唔知你講咩<br />\ncell(row, column) 唔係就控制到邊格咩"},{"pid":"c311451290ae9f493d1c5b3df9999f67741b4b35","tid":711041,"uid":43724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想幫但唔知你講咩<br />\ncells(row, column) 唔係就控制到邊格咩</blockquote>"},{"pid":"321f682c2b10c52aa1cec840caa8220a5b6cd429","tid":711041,"uid":168540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c311451290ae9f493d1c5b3df9999f67741b4b35","tid":711041,"uid":43724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想幫但唔知你講咩<br />\ncells(row, column) 唔係就控制到邊格咩</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:24:44.000Z","msg":"Sor 表達得差,<br />\n<br />\nSub rqw()<br />\n<br />\nFor j = 1 To 99<br />\n<br />\nCells(100, i).Value = &quot;=sum(&quot;唔識寫&quot;)<br />\n<br />\nNext j<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEnd Sub<br />\n<br />\n唔識寫右手邊,A100呢格= A1至A99+埋咁<br />\n因為一入B既時候 , 右邊又J1:J99 我又冇理由 CELLS (1,j)+....咁寫好似唔係好識Refer,唔該晒"},{"pid":"2470accf9fb8661aa57095cd82790c3baef9d755","tid":711041,"uid":46726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"321f682c2b10c52aa1cec840caa8220a5b6cd429","tid":711041,"uid":168540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c311451290ae9f493d1c5b3df9999f67741b4b35","tid":711041,"uid":43724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想幫但唔知你講咩<br />\ncells(row, column) 唔係就控制到邊格咩</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:24:44.000Z","msg":"Sor 表達得差,<br />\n<br />\nSub rqw()<br />\n<br />\nFor j = 1 To 99<br />\n<br />\nCells(100, i).Value = &quot;=sum(&quot;唔識寫&quot;)<br />\n<br />\nNext j<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEnd Sub<br />\n<br />\n唔識寫右手邊,A100呢格= A1至A99+埋咁<br />\n因為一入B既時候 , 右邊又J1:J99 我又冇理由 CELLS (1,j)+....咁寫好似唔係好識Refer,唔該晒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:42:07.000Z","msg":"Cells(100, i).Formula = &quot;=SUM(A1:B1)&quot;"},{"pid":"48b6331c18fa0102a752592d3033fedec1c7c65c","tid":711041,"uid":168540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2470accf9fb8661aa57095cd82790c3baef9d755","tid":711041,"uid":46726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"321f682c2b10c52aa1cec840caa8220a5b6cd429","tid":711041,"uid":168540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c311451290ae9f493d1c5b3df9999f67741b4b35","tid":711041,"uid":43724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T08:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想幫但唔知你講咩<br />\ncells(row, column) 唔係就控制到邊格咩</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:24:44.000Z","msg":"Sor 表達得差,<br />\n<br />\nSub rqw()<br />\n<br />\nFor j = 1 To 99<br />\n<br />\nCells(100, i).Value = &quot;=sum(&quot;唔識寫&quot;)<br />\n<br />\nNext j<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEnd Sub<br />\n<br />\n唔識寫右手邊,A100呢格= A1至A99+埋咁<br />\n因為一入B既時候 , 右邊又J1:J99 我又冇理由 CELLS (1,j)+....咁寫好似唔係好識Refer,唔該晒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:42:07.000Z","msg":"Cells(100, i).Formula = &quot;=SUM(A1:B1)&quot;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:48:09.000Z","msg":"咁咪全部都係A1+B1囉? 我要 第1個ITERATION A1+...+A99<br />\n 第2個ITERATION B1+...+B99   ......"},{"pid":"fa4a739d734113edec998855cecc521d354de4b0","tid":711041,"uid":125895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:25:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想幫但唔知你講咩<br />\ncells(row, column) 唔係就控制到邊格咩</blockquote></blockquote>Sor 表達得差,<br />\n<br />\nSub rqw()<br />\n<br />\nFor j = 1 To 99<br />\n<br />\nCells(100, i).Value = &quot;=sum(&quot;唔識寫&quot;)<br />\n<br />\nNext j<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEnd Sub<br />\n<br />\n唔識寫右手邊,A100呢格= A1至A99+埋咁<br />\n因為一入B既時候 , 右邊又J1:J99 我又冇理由 CELLS (1,j)+....咁寫好似唔係好識Refer,唔該晒</blockquote>Cells(100, i).Formula = &quot;=SUM(A1:B1)&quot;</blockquote>咁咪全部都係A1+B1囉? 我要 第1個ITERATION A1+...+A99<br />\n 第2個ITERATION B1+...+B99   ......</blockquote><br />\ninteger to character"},{"pid":"583d71c5f34195f2f9e77f6ddb76452c1ddbcd01","tid":711041,"uid":161095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:17:57.000Z","msg":"你係想噤?<br />\n<br />\nA100 = sum(A1:A99)<br />\nB100 = sum(B1:B99)<br />\nC100 = sum(C1:C99)<br />\nD100 = sum(D1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />99)<br />\n....<br />\n....<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但你for j 做乜鳩?<br />\n應該係for i<br />\n<br />\n假設你有10 個columns<br />\n<br />\n類似噤... <br />\n<br />\nSub rqw()<br />\n<br />\nFor j = 1 To 10<br />\n<br />\nCells(100, i).Value = &quot;=SUM( Range(Cells(1, i), Cells(99, i))&quot;<br />\n<br />\nNext i<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEnd Sub<br />\n<br />\n可能記錯syntax... 太耐無用..."},{"pid":"56a8f017fd13d7697cfb89b88f16b2ad12bfecbe","tid":711041,"uid":161095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:19:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係想噤?<br />\n<br />\nA100 = sum(A1:A99)<br />\nB100 = sum(B1:B99)<br />\nC100 = sum(C1:C99)<br />\nD100 = sum(D1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />99)<br />\n....<br />\n....<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但你for j 做乜鳩?<br />\n應該係for i<br />\n<br />\n假設你有10 個columns<br />\n<br />\n類似噤... <br />\n<br />\nSub rqw()<br />\n<br />\nFor <span style=\"color: red;\">i</span> = 1 To 10<br />\n<br />\nCells(100, i).Value = &quot;=SUM( Range(Cells(1, i), Cells(99, i))&quot;<br />\n<br />\nNext i<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEnd Sub<br />\n<br />\n可能記錯syntax... 太耐無用...</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f338a1599700dd2d54d8c14a6d2e9f7a97e0c46e","tid":711041,"uid":78751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T09:42:21.000Z","msg":"自己錄個macro 咪知點code<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421b6263aad729b72b9aae345005bab5dec8ccaa","tid":711041,"uid":7093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T09:48:35.000Z","msg":"用FormulaR1C1 做relative reference"},{"pid":"faa42ae4cb083dbea5f865c37de6b8934d835bf2","tid":711041,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T10:25:27.000Z","msg":"X = Cell(R,C).row<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"118a2d0496caefd38324367612900ebd1792c8bd","tid":711041,"uid":136955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:00:08.000Z","msg":"<code>\n\n</code>"},{"pid":"859b40beecfe1c22163f807d1f033bae4252da23","tid":711041,"uid":185693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T17:03:55.000Z","msg":"你在cell(A100) 輸入 &ldquo;=sum(A2:A99)&quot;<br />\n再用fill by formula <br />\n<a href=\"https://support.office.com/en-us/article/fill-a-formula-down-into-adjacent-cells-041edfe2-05bc-40e6-b933-ef48c3f308c6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.office.com%2Fen-us%2Farticle%2Ffill-a-formula-down-into-adjacent-cells-041edfe2-05bc-40e6-b933-ef48c3f308c6&d=TIjPz5sjqPVI6l%2FEJ%2BrCdP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=50e009fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.office.com/en-us/article/fill-a-formula-down-into-adjacent-cells-041edfe2-05bc-40e6-b933-ef48c3f308c6</a><br />\n<br />\nVba 都唔洗寫"},{"pid":"c2e1cc3082ec16e243303b6a90f4905e41b18c2c","tid":711041,"uid":168540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56a8f017fd13d7697cfb89b88f16b2ad12bfecbe","tid":711041,"uid":161095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:19:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係想噤?<br />\n<br />\nA100 = sum(A1:A99)<br />\nB100 = sum(B1:B99)<br />\nC100 = sum(C1:C99)<br />\nD100 = sum(D1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />99)<br />\n....<br />\n....<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但你for j 做乜鳩?<br />\n應該係for i<br />\n<br />\n假設你有10 個columns<br />\n<br />\n類似噤... <br />\n<br />\nSub rqw()<br />\n<br />\nFor <span style=\"color: red;\">i</span> = 1 To 10<br />\n<br />\nCells(100, i).Value = &quot;=SUM( Range(Cells(1, i), Cells(99, i))&quot;<br />\n<br />\nNext i<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEnd Sub<br />\n<br />\n可能記錯syntax... 太耐無用...</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:04:18.000Z","msg":"多謝CHING, 但整唔到"},{"pid":"5461c34e181637d73a9f1fe1b402604f05a84595","tid":711041,"uid":168540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f338a1599700dd2d54d8c14a6d2e9f7a97e0c46e","tid":711041,"uid":78751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T09:42:21.000Z","msg":"自己錄個macro 咪知點code<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:05:14.000Z","msg":"Thanks 但For loop 入面 應該record唔到呀嘛?　"},{"pid":"7624ae0275b5d4798c66a9b9f5f6e3fdd9d89bfd","tid":711041,"uid":168540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"421b6263aad729b72b9aae345005bab5dec8ccaa","tid":711041,"uid":7093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T09:48:35.000Z","msg":"用FormulaR1C1 做relative reference"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:05:34.000Z","msg":"研究下先感謝"},{"pid":"94cbca2fa646d42315769857e53045ed885dcc00","tid":711041,"uid":168540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"faa42ae4cb083dbea5f865c37de6b8934d835bf2","tid":711041,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T10:25:27.000Z","msg":"X = Cell(R,C).row<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:08:17.000Z","msg":"我想入面跟住郁, <br />\n<br />\nA100= SUM(A1:A99)<br />\nobtain左個row, 但無理由寫到 (i)1:(i)99咁<br />\n<br />\nCELLS 個到又指定晒個格, 卡左關"},{"pid":"8b9804e227e7e54d4064edc7f5cc1bed5e76cd03","tid":711041,"uid":168540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"859b40beecfe1c22163f807d1f033bae4252da23","tid":711041,"uid":185693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T17:03:55.000Z","msg":"你在cell(A100) 輸入 &ldquo;=sum(A2:A99)&quot;<br />\n再用fill by formula <br />\n<a href=\"https://support.office.com/en-us/article/fill-a-formula-down-into-adjacent-cells-041edfe2-05bc-40e6-b933-ef48c3f308c6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.office.com%2Fen-us%2Farticle%2Ffill-a-formula-down-into-adjacent-cells-041edfe2-05bc-40e6-b933-ef48c3f308c6&d=TIjPz5sjqPVI6l%2FEJ%2BrCdP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=50e009fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://support.office.com/en-us/article/fill-a-formula-down-into-adjacent-cells-041edfe2-05bc-40e6-b933-ef48c3f308c6</a><br />\n<br />\nVba 都唔洗寫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:12:13.000Z","msg":"我睇過應該等於就咁拉? 因為我呢個只係例子, 有好多步驟, 打算啪入去一次過做"},{"pid":"a741ee3c5b491a9de2b15c0f23c5ffdb5906937c","tid":711041,"uid":3318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:27:55.000Z","msg":"For i = 1 to 10<br />\ncells(100,i).formular1c1 = &ldquo;=sum(r[-99]c:r[-1]c)&rdquo;<br />\nnext i"},{"pid":"c549b914a828fc8ab186addaf03e32b17a4c7370","tid":711041,"uid":185693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T16:03:18.000Z","msg":"用A1 notation<br />\n<br />\nFor i = 1 to 10<br />\ncells(100,i).value = &ldquo;=sum(&quot;&amp;RANGE(&quot;A1:A99&quot;).offset(0,i).address&amp; &quot;)&rdquo;<br />\nnext i"},{"pid":"9885bf885774ae7c418667ea3fb788af0e596fb6","tid":711041,"uid":185693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo